{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_10_02",
  "title": "兵藤雫 2話 イタズラ好きな猫",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "アリス役に決まった次の日、学校に行ったら……\n私、アリスの役から……木の役に、かわっちゃったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The day after it was decided I’d play Alice‚ when I went to school…\nI was changed from the role of Alice… to the role of a tree.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.1400682767
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしてそんなことに……！？\n雫はアリスを演じるのを楽しみにしてたんだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-why did that happen…!?\nYou were looking forward to playing Alice‚ weren’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.0400684198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.4573693275
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.7073693275
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "うん、すっごく楽しみで、わくわくしてた……でも\n私がアリス役に指名されたのは、たまたまだったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I was really excited… but\nI was only chosen as Alice by coincidence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.5805660883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "本気でアリスを演じたいっていうクラスメイトの子が\n次の日、「自分がやりたい」って……立候補して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A classmate who seriously wanted to play Alice\nsaid the next day‚ “I want to do it‚” and volunteered.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8805660883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "その子の凄く一生懸命な目を見て……\n私、自分から、役を譲っちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I saw how earnest her eyes were…\nI gave her the role myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.3138994216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.3804759661
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.3804759661
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのか。雫だってやりたかったのに……\n……でも、言えなかったんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Even though you wanted to do it too…\n…you couldn’t say it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.4666664759,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "うん。あの頃は、今よりもずっと、控えめで……\n自分の気持ちも、上手に話せなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Back then‚ I was much more reserved than I am now…\nI couldn’t express my feelings very well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.2885021526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.9247391382
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "結局、その子と交代で、木の役になったんだけど\n……その後、もっと困っちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the end‚ I switched with her and became the tree.\n…but after that‚ things got even harder.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.521835486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.5180725414
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それだけでも辛かっただろうに、まだ何か起こるのか？\n……あ、それってもしかして、従姉妹の……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That alone must’ve been painful—did something else happen too?\n…Ah‚ could it be about your cousin…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.1670358553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "そう……お姉ちゃんにアリスをやる、って言った時\n本当に、すっごく喜んでくれた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… when I told my older sister I’d be playing Alice‚\nshe was really‚ truly happy for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.7204742748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.7959860801
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "だから……その次の日に、木の役になっちゃったって\nアリスの役を譲っちゃった、なんて……言えなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So… when the next day I became the tree instead‚\nI couldn’t tell her I’d given up the role of Alice…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.3538076082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.3511790911
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "雫の気持ちは分かるよ。俺だって雫と同じ立場だったら\n言えなかったと思う。それからどうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand how you felt. If I were in your position‚\nI don’t think I could’ve said it either. What did you do after that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.6999998092,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "私は……最後まで、何も言わないことにした\n劇を観られなければ、バレないと思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… decided not to say anything until the end.\nI thought if she couldn’t see the play‚ she wouldn’t know…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.984850184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.3222904205
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "劇の発表の日を、お姉ちゃんに伝えなかった\nお母さん達にも、内緒にしてってお願いした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn’t tell her the date of the performance.\nI asked my parents to keep it a secret as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.784850184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "内緒って、辛いことなんだって……分かった\n嘘をつくのと同じくらい、胸が重くて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s when I realized how painful it is to keep a secret…\nIt weighed on my heart‚ just like lying…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.9850619918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.4322887104
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "本当は、アリスがやりたいって気持ちも\nアリスを譲っちゃったことも、内緒にして……苦しくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both my true wish to play Alice‚ and the fact\nthat I gave the role up—I kept them hidden… and it was painful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.2730479434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.0707782747
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.3207782747
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "それでも、本番の日はきちゃった。その日は朝から……\n緊張で、倒れそうだった。木の役、だけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ the day of the performance came. From the morning…\nI was so nervous‚ I felt like I might collapse. It was just the role of a tree…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.7515239714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "なんとか……木の役をやりきろうと思って\n心を落ち着けて、ステージの上に、立った……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but I told myself I’d somehow see it through.\nI calmed myself and stood on the stage…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.2515239714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.1996903104
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "でも木になりきって、静かに客席の方を見ていたら……\nそこに、お姉ちゃんが……いたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But as I fully became the tree and quietly looked toward the audience…\nmy cousin… was there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.9181906381,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 173.8496902151
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 173.8496902151
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "木なのに……悲鳴を上げそうに、なった\n頭の中はぐるぐるするし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though I was a tree… I almost screamed.\nMy head was spinning…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.6848573047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 181.4266966822
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、それだけじゃなくて、実際に倒れちゃった……\n木の役から、倒木の役になっちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ not just that—I actually collapsed…\nI went from playing a tree to a fallen tree…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.5515239714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 190.3841119451
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "うまいことを言ったな……じゃなくて\n倒れた時、怪我はなかったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was a clever way to put it… no wait—\nWere you hurt when you collapsed?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.1999977747,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-szk018.m4a",
      "text": "うん、平気だった……\nすぐ保健室に連れて行かれて、お母さんと帰った",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I was okay…\nI was taken to the nurse’s office right away and went home with my mom.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.7957412718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 204.862570286
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
