      "text": "私……この過去を、やり直したい\nせっかくもう一度、舞台に、立てるんだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… want to redo this past.\nSince I… finally… get to stand on stage again…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.5624079385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-szk020.m4a",
      "text": "今度は、主役もやりたいって、言えた\n譲っちゃいそうにもなったけど、胸を張って言えた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "this time I was able to say… I want the lead role too.\nI almost gave it up again‚ but I said it with my head held high.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 216.7957412718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 221.0864026709
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
