      "text": "すずちゃんと私の、ダブル主演\n胸を張って、誇れる……いい舞台にしたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A double lead with Suzu-chan and me.\nI want it to be a stage… I can truly be proud of.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.5957412718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
