      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それが雫の心残り、か。教えてくれてありがとう\nその舞台、例の従姉妹のお姉さんも観に来るのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that was your lingering regret. Thank you for telling me.\nWill that cousin you mentioned come to see the play too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 235.0666644413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
