      "text": "うん、連絡は、した……チケットも送る\n今回はちゃんとした舞台を観せられたら……嬉しい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I contacted her… I’ll send her a ticket too.\nThis time‚ if I can show her a proper stage… I’ll be happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.9403895059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
