      "text": "雫とすずは、ダブル主演でダブルキャストだったな\nお互いにアリスで、チェシャ猫だっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You and Suzu were double leads and double-cast‚ right?\nEach of you plays Alice and the Cheshire Cat.",
